reviewText: Very speedy delivery! Packaged like it was brand new. All the discs played with no problems.
I bought this for my husband for Christmas, so it hasn't been opened yet.  It was just as described and shipped in a timely fashion.
Very much pleased.
The DVDs were in pristine condition, the cases were perfect! Can't wait for season 5!
It's A Great Season to be sure. Can't wait for Season 5.
The entertainment continues in this saga about the walking dead people and the walking live people.  I wonder where they're going with this and for how long because I really like this series.
Watched this show from day one. I can say this much for The Walking Dead....It keeps you guessing what happens next. Always a surprised around every corner. Never a disappointment!
I love the show, but the DVD I received has a few frozen spots.
This product was very low on quality I think I received a copy of the original the discs played with a very distorted picture
dvd sticks and cuts out 2 dvds didn't play at all
great
disk 4 and disk 5 were distorted and damaged.
Wow...! So happy with my brand new TWD DVD 4th season. This completes my collection, as the cast of seasons 1-4 are my extended family. :)
The group dynamics and how each person's philosophy of life changes continues to fascinate me.

Everything arrived by the date specified and all the episodes played without any issue.  I was somewhat concerned and some of the other reviews said the  disk jumped around but that wasn't my experience , everything was great.
thumbs up

Very happy with purchase.

This was a great season! I loved the way all the characters got to grow in their storylines. Can't wait for the next season.
